{"TopicId":149871,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Thread Permalinks?","CreatedByName":"micha","CreatedById":113840,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T09:25:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"micha","CreatedById":113840,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T09:25:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the original forum software it was possible to link to a thread by an ID (not the full title). Those old links still work, so I guess it must be possible, but I can\u0027t find a way to get a permalink using the current forum software.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUse-case is that a lot of mod-threads get updated as the mod gets updated, including their title. Hence it would be nice to be able to link to a thread using its thread-id rather than the full link.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0- Micha.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: Add example (and yes, I tried to use the \u0022topic number\u0022 as a thread-id for other threads but it doesn\u0027t work):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOld Permalink thread link: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/81578\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/81578\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame thread as new-style: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723-090-orbital-material-science-version-06/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723-090-orbital-material-science-version-06/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-13T10:38:23Z\u0022 title=\u002210/13/2016 10:38  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 13, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by micha\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eadd examples\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"micha","CreatedById":113840,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T10:37:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWorked out how to convert the new-style links to a permalink using only the topic-id (continuing on from my examples above):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/81578\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?showtopic=73723\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWould be nice to have a \u0022Share this Thread\u0022 button (similar to \u0022Share this Post\u0022) which generates this universal URL.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T13:33:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nChanging the title doesn\u0027t affect those links working. Example: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723-Mechjeb-being-added-to-stock-OMG-the-sky-is-falling\u0022 ipsnoembed=\u0022true\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723-Mechjeb-being-added-to-stock-OMG-the-sky-is-falling\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne quirk is that it doesn\u0027t work if you omit the title altogether, \u003Cem\u003Esomething\u003C/em\u003E must be there. So this won\u0027t work:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723\u0022 ipsnoembed=\u0022true\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723\u003C/a\u003E but this will: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723-A\u0022 ipsnoembed=\u0022true\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/73723-A\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWasn\u0027t aware of the ?showtopic=id trick, thanks for that. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"micha","CreatedById":113840,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T13:36:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHmm, fairly certain I broke my thread-links by changing a thread title the other day.\u00A0 I blame man-flu. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T21:33:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222801763\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149871\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221476365635\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWasn\u0027t aware of the ?showtopic=id trick, thanks for that. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167737\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@UomoCapra\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0or \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Badie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0could look at that and maybe make it the default for links. I think that would be good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T21:35:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222802554\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149871\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221476394398\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167737\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167737-uomocapra/\u0022 id=\u0022ips_uid_5345_5\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@UomoCapra\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0or \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Badie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0could look at that and maybe make it the default for links. I think that would be good.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut why? It\u0027s a change that would have to be made every time the forum software is updated (assuming it can be done at all), and the current links work fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"legoclone09","CreatedById":142607,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-13T21:36:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222802558\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149871\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221476394507\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut why? It\u0027s a change that would have to be made every time the forum software is updated (assuming it can be done at all), and the current links work fine.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe normal links are really long for me, but maybe have it be part of a \u0027share link\u0027, like how the normal thread URL in the omnibox stays the same and a \u0027share\u0027 link might be the ?showthread=\u0022id\u0022, kind of how YouTube has youtube.com and youtu.be.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}